OL,3,CRoadworks begin on main route in Durham
OL,5,FRoadworks are to begin on a main route
OL,6,Finto Durham in order to remove
OL,7,Ftemporary bus stops, repair footpaths
OL,8,Fand railings following the reopening
OL,9,Fof the bus station earlier this year.
OL,11,FThe county council will carry out the
OL,12,Fworks on North Road and Crossgate
OL,13,FPeth, towards the Milburngate
OL,14,Froundabout for 14 weeks.
OL,16,FIn addition, benches will be
OL,17,Frefurbished, lamppost banners to
OL,18,Fpromote upcoming events and festivals
OL,19,Fwill be installed, along with street
OL,20,Flighting which will project images and
OL,21,Fpatterns onto the pavement.
