OL,3,CRoadworks begin on main route in Durham
OL,5,FThe work will be carried out in phases
OL,6,Fin order to minimise disruption, with
OL,7,Fsigns in place to divert traffic.
OL,9,FCllr John Shuttleworth, is the Durham
OL,10,FCounty Council's Cabinet member for
OL,11,Fhighways, community safety and rural
OL,12,Fcommunities. He said: "North Road is
OL,13,Fthe gateway to the historic city of
OL,14,FDurham and is the first area many
OL,15,Fvisitors see if they arrive by bus or
OL,16,Ftrain.
