OL,3,CRoadworks begin on main route in Durham
OL,5,F"The enhancements are the final stage
OL,6,Fof works that have already delivered
OL,7,Fthe new Durham Bus Station and we want
OL,8,Fto take this opportunity to regenerate
OL,9,FNorth Road andgive it a more modern
OL,10,Fand welcoming first impression.
OL,12,F"The work will reinforce Durham's
OL,13,Fstanding as a thriving place to visit;
OL,14,Fhelping attract residents, visitors
OL,15,Fand shoppers to the city and
OL,16,Fsupporting our independent businesses."
OL,18,FThe first phase will begin today (23
OL,19,FJune 2024), and will start opposite
OL,20,Fthe bus station, going up towards the
OL,21,FNorth Road roundabout.
