OL,3,CRoadworks begin on main route in Durham
OL,5,FThis will take approximately seven
OL,6,Fweeks and during this time only buses
OL,7,Fwill be able to turn right out of the
OL,8,Fstation. There also will be restricted
OL,9,Faccess to vehicles between 9am and 5pm.
OL,11,FOnce the first phase is complete, the
OL,12,Fsecond phase will begin from the bus
OL,13,Fstation towards Crossgate Peth for
OL,14,Fanother further seven weeks.
OL,16,FDuring the works, bus passengers are
OL,17,Fbeing advised to check their travel
OL,18,Fplans as some routes are being
OL,19,Fslightly altered.
